   clear
   export PS1="\e[1;33m\$ \e[m"
   RED='\033[0;31m'
  echo -e " ${RED}     =========================        "
  echo "      |                       |"
   echo "      |     £iñüx-Terminal    |"
  echo "      |                       |"
  echo "      ========================="


Paste above code in .bashrc file in termux home directory , you will get new look to your termux

